ol.li:
Create the diskquota database. The diskquota module
          uses this database to store the list of databases where the module is enabled.
          $ createdb diskquota;

Create the diskquota extension in the
          database.=# CREATE EXTENSION diskquota;
CREATE EXTENSION

 Create the s1
          schema.=# CREATE SCHEMA s1;
CREATE SCHEMA

The following commands create a table in the s1 schema and insert a
          small amount of data into it. The schema has no data yet, so it is not on the denylist.
          =# SET search_path TO s1;
SET
=# CREATE TABLE a(i int);
CREATE TABLE
=# INSERT INTO a SELECT generate_series(1,100);
INSERT 0 100
